OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest into 'final
OL,4,Cstages'
OL,6,FOn Monday morning, the jury was told
OL,7,Fthe proceedings were in the "final
OL,8,Fstages" by coroner Mr Justice Rooney
OL,9,Fas they were released for the day.
OL,11,FIt came after counsel to the coroner
OL,12,FPeter Coll KC read out an agreed
OL,13,Fposition relating to the measurements
OL,14,Fand dimensions of an 11-bar security
OL,15,Fgrill on the culvert.
OL,17,FHe said this "concludes the evidence"
OL,18,Fthey were likely to hear.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@GO]yD@NOUyD@eO]
